title: Rocko - U.O.E.N.O. (Tootie Single Edit)
description:
Technical details:
MP3 V0, 44.1khz
Length: 4:23

This is a combination of two lossy mixes of this song, edited in order to create the "original" mix without the added mixtape effects.

The Rick Ross verse *may* be surrounded by mixtape effects. I'm not sure if the female voice is part of the track or not, but transparently removing it seems not feasibly possible.

The best versions of the tracks I discovered were used, but they were MP3s; as such this MP3 can be considered transcoded. I'm not aware of any lossless release of this song, so it is what it is.
